		<title>19Religion in the area.</title>
		<content>                                       
  Scotton and Farnham are included in  
 the Parish of Farnham with Scotton,   
 Stavely, Copgrove and Arkendale.      
                                       
  At Farnham Parish Church, services   
 are held monthly with a fairly large  
 congregation. The vicar of Farnham    
 trained for the church on a part-time 
 basis, going to college one day a     
 week.                                 
                                       
  Scotton Methodist Chapel has weekly  
 evening services and a monthly morning
 service.                              
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
                                       
